1
02:34:48,944 --> 02:34:49,958
THORIN:
Anything?

2
02:34:50,208 --> 02:34:51,710
DWALIN:
Nothing!

3
02:34:55,505 --> 02:34:59,647
THORIN: If the map is true,
then the hidden door lies directly above us.

4
02:35:04,681 --> 02:35:06,308
BILBO:
Up here!

5
02:35:14,691 --> 02:35:17,152
You have keen eyes, Master Baggins.

6
02:35:33,043 --> 02:35:34,961
[GRUNTING]

7
02:35:44,805 --> 02:35:46,098
[PANTS]

8
02:35:48,845 --> 02:35:50,101
THORIN:
This must be it.

9
02:35:52,312 --> 02:35:53,814
The hidden door.

10
02:35:58,068 --> 02:35:59,820
THORIN:
Let all those who doubted us...

11
02:36:00,987 --> 02:36:02,322
...rue this day!

12
02:36:02,572 --> 02:36:04,572
[ALL CHEERING]

13
02:36:08,036 --> 02:36:10,497
Right, then. We have a key.

14
02:36:12,207 --> 02:36:13,708
Which means that somewhere...

15
02:36:14,835 --> 02:36:16,211
...there is a key-hole.

16
02:36:16,920 --> 02:36:19,820
THORIN:
"The last light of Durin's Day...

17
02:36:21,800 --> 02:36:24,302
...will shine upon the key-hole."

18
02:36:33,436 --> 02:36:34,521
Nori.

19
02:36:38,191 --> 02:36:39,693
[DWALIN GRUNTING]

20
02:36:41,153 --> 02:36:43,113
We're losing the light. Come on.

21
02:36:49,619 --> 02:36:52,205
NORI:
Be quiet! I can't hear when you're thumping.

22
02:36:52,338 --> 02:36:53,640
I can't find it.

23
02:36:54,708 --> 02:36:57,377
It's not here!
It's not! Here!

24
02:36:58,941 --> 02:37:00,441
THORIN: Break it down!
DWALIN: Aye.

25
02:37:02,049 --> 02:37:03,049
Come on!

26
02:37:05,035 --> 02:37:05,927
DWALIN:
Break!

27
02:37:06,178 --> 02:37:07,489
It has to break.

28
02:37:08,138 --> 02:37:09,472
BALIN:
It's no good.

29
02:37:09,723 --> 02:37:12,225
The door's sealed. Can't be opened by force.

30
02:37:13,852 --> 02:37:15,329
There's a powerful magic on it.

31
02:37:24,613 --> 02:37:25,739
No!

32
02:37:31,077 --> 02:37:33,371
"The last light of Durin's Day...

33
02:37:35,248 --> 02:37:37,006
...will shine upon the key-hole."

34
02:37:41,254 --> 02:37:42,839
That is what it says.

35
02:37:47,344 --> 02:37:48,762
What did we miss?

36
02:37:52,724 --> 02:37:54,184
What did we miss?

37
02:37:55,227 --> 02:37:56,186
Balin?

38
02:37:56,811 --> 02:37:58,521
We've lost the light.

39
02:38:01,066 --> 02:38:02,901
There's no more to be done.

40
02:38:04,444 --> 02:38:06,529
<i>We had but one chance.</i>

41
02:38:08,949 --> 02:38:10,200
<i>Come away, lads.</i>

42
02:38:10,450 --> 02:38:12,244
It's over.

43
02:38:13,328 --> 02:38:15,455
- Wait a minute.
GLOIN: We're too late.

44
02:38:17,958 --> 02:38:19,376
BILBO:
Where are they going?

45
02:38:21,169 --> 02:38:23,046
You can't give up now!

46
02:38:37,978 --> 02:38:39,145
Thorin.

47
02:38:41,189 --> 02:38:42,857
You can't give up now.

48
02:38:54,411 --> 02:38:56,788
"Stand by the gray stone...

49
02:38:58,665 --> 02:39:00,750
...when the thrush knocks."

50
02:39:01,501 --> 02:39:02,877
The setting sun.

51
02:39:03,920 --> 02:39:06,798
And "the last light of Durin's Day
will shine..."

52
02:39:08,299 --> 02:39:09,759
The last light.

53
02:39:12,303 --> 02:39:13,680
Last light.

54
02:39:28,062 --> 02:39:33,062
[CLICKING ON STONE]

55
02:39:50,383 --> 02:39:51,634
The last light!

56
02:40:01,853 --> 02:40:02,979
The key-hole!

57
02:40:03,683 --> 02:40:04,556
<i>Come back!</i>

58
02:40:04,777 --> 02:40:06,112
Come back!

59
02:40:06,244 --> 02:40:10,222
It's the light of the moon!
The last moon of autumn!

60
02:40:10,713 --> 02:40:11,946
Ha, ha, ha!

61
02:40:13,865 --> 02:40:16,242
Where's the key? Where's the key?
Where's the--?

62
02:40:16,493 --> 02:40:18,203
It was here.

63
02:40:18,453 --> 02:40:20,246
Come on, it was-- It was here.

64
02:40:20,955 --> 02:40:21,963
It was just--

65
02:40:22,533 --> 02:40:23,533
[TINKLING]

66
02:40:57,826 --> 02:40:59,076
[THUMP]

67
02:41:19,806 --> 02:41:21,266
Erebor.

68
02:41:21,975 --> 02:41:23,101
Thorin.

69
02:41:36,489 --> 02:41:38,366
I know these walls.

70
02:41:42,120 --> 02:41:43,663
These halls.

71
02:41:46,666 --> 02:41:48,042
This stone.

72
02:41:51,963 --> 02:41:53,965
You remember it, Balin.

73
02:41:57,594 --> 02:42:00,096
Chambers filled with golden light.

74
02:42:01,973 --> 02:42:03,474
I remember.

75
02:42:16,738 --> 02:42:21,618
"Herein lies the Seventh
Kingdom of Durin's Folk.

76
02:42:23,578 --> 02:42:27,625
May the Heart of the Mountain
unite all Dwarves...

77
02:42:28,012 --> 02:42:30,501
...in defense of this home."

78
02:42:32,212 --> 02:42:34,047
The Throne of the King.

79
02:42:34,714 --> 02:42:36,049
- Ah.

80
02:42:37,759 --> 02:42:41,095
And what's that above it?

81
02:42:44,641 --> 02:42:46,392
The Arkenstone.

82
02:42:47,685 --> 02:42:49,103
Arkenstone.

83
02:42:53,024 --> 02:42:54,359
And what's that?

84
02:42:54,692 --> 02:42:57,654
That, Master Burglar...

85
02:42:58,696 --> 02:43:00,740
...is why you are here.

